adding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mopcon 2019 26\"\n        title=\"mopcon 2019 26\"\n        src=\"/static/102382e448d00f710e37d204635ca57d/8a6f4/mopcon-2019-26.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/102382e448d00f710e37d204635ca57d/51f8b/mopcon-2019-26.jpg 180w,\n/static/102382e448d00f710e37d204635ca57d/5aea8/mopcon-2019-26.jpg 360w,\n/static/102382e448d00f710e37d204635ca57d/8a6f4/mopcon-2019-26.jpg 720w,\n/static/102382e448d00f710e37d204635ca57d/f7125/mopcon-2019-26.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>好吃不貴，很多日韓觀光客來吃；很妙的是攤位牆上有放低音量的標語，避免吵到隔壁住戶睡午覺</p>\n<hr>\n<h3>一頁商店「從零到千萬營收創業故事」光速火箭有限公司 Young Boss 李冠霆</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mopcon 2019 27\"\n        title=\"mopcon 2019 27\"\n        src=\"/static/dd1b384a48447cb3e329eb316a89ea62/8a6f4/mopcon-2019-27.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dd1b384a48447cb3e329eb316a89ea62/51f8b/mopcon-2019-27.jpg 180w,\n/static/dd1b384a48447cb3e329eb316a89ea62/5aea8/mopcon-2019-27.jpg 360w,\n/static/dd1b384a48447cb3e329eb316a89ea62/8a6f4/mopcon-2019-27.jpg 720w,\n/static/dd1b384a48447cb3e329eb316a89ea62/f7125/mopcon-2019-27.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>講者商業思路清淅，非常有經營理念</p>\n<hr>\n<h3>一頁商店「從零到千萬營收創業故事」</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70.859375%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mopcon 2019 28\"\n        title=\"mopcon 2019 28\"\n        src=\"/static/b5791a30a09e959949a894d80d9f7641/8a6f4/mopcon-2019-28.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b5791a30a09e959949a894d80d9f7641/51f8b/mopcon-2019-28.jpg 180w,\n/static/b5791a30a09e959949a894d80d9f7641/5aea8/mopcon-2019-28.jpg 360w,\n/static/b5791a30a09e959949a894d80d9f7641/8a6f4/mopcon-2019-28.jpg 720w,\n/static/b5791a30a09e959949a894d80d9f7641/72109/mopcon-2019-28.jpg 1080w,\n/static/b5791a30a09e959949a894d80d9f7641/92a9d/mopcon-2019-28.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3><a href=\"https://github.com/sudoliyang\">@sudoliyang</a> 跟 李冠霆 合照</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mopcon 2019 29\"\n        title=\"mopcon 2019 29\"\n        src=\"/static/ed1a84c87d6985d9c9dc7652e6af78b7/8a6f4/mopcon-2019-29.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ed1a84c87d6985d9c9dc7652e6af78b7/51f8b/mopcon-2019-29.jpg 180w,\n/static/ed1a84c87d6985d9c9dc7652e6af78b7/5aea8/mopcon-2019-29.jpg 360w,\n/static/ed1a84c87d6985d9c9dc7652e6af78b7/8a6f4/mopcon-2019-29.jpg 720w,\n/static/ed1a84c87d6985d9c9dc7652e6af78b7/f7125/mopcon-2019-29.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/agile.kaohsiung/\">Agile Kaohsiung</a> 攤位</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mopcon 2019 30\"\n        title=\"mopcon 2019 30\"\n        src=\"/static/cfa6ca993ccb976dfee4c9db689f5943/8a6f4/mopcon-2019-30.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cfa6ca993ccb976dfee4c9db689f5943/51f8b/mopcon-2019-30.jpg 180w,\n/static/cfa6ca993ccb976dfee4c9db689f5943/5aea8/mopcon-2019-30.jpg 360w,\n/static/cfa6ca993ccb976dfee4c9db689f5943/8a6f4/mopcon-2019-30.jpg 720w,\n/static/cfa6ca993ccb976dfee4c9db689f5943/72109/mopcon-2019-30.jpg 1080w,\n/static/cfa6ca993ccb976dfee4c9db689f5943/92a9d/mopcon-2019-30.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>拿了一些很通的貼紙跟<strong>很漂亮</strong>的敏捷海報</p>\n<hr>\n<h3>「敏捷論壇 - 不同世代的敏捷推行之道」</h3>\n<p>由右至左</p>\n<ul>\n<li>新加坡商鈦坦科技 總經理 李境展</li>\n<li>91App Scrum Master/QA manager 王泰瑞</li>\n<li>中佑資訊 工程師 江佳佳</li>\n<li>一卡通票證 敏捷轉型顧問 張昀煒</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mopcon 2019 31\"\n        title=\"mopcon 2019 31\"\n        src=\"/static/689afa7ab34c62519d293a50c44ef72c/8a6f4/mopcon-2019-31.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/689afa7ab34c62519d293a50c44ef72c/51f8b/mopcon-2019-31.jpg 180w,\n/static/689afa7ab34c62519d293a50c44ef72c/5aea8/mopcon-2019-31.jpg 360w,\n/static/689afa7ab34c62519d293a50c44ef72c/8a6f4/mopcon-2019-31.jpg 720w,\n/static/689afa7ab34c62519d293a50c44ef72c/72109/mopcon-2019-31.jpg 1080w,\n/static/689afa7ab34c62519d293a50c44ef72c/92a9d/mopcon-2019-31.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>進到議場才發現剛剛在攤位聊的是這場的講者 XD 問的問題都得到很好的解答，得到很多幫助！</p>\n<hr>\n<h3>Unconference 分享遠端資料工程師的經驗</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mopcon 2019 32\"\n        title=\"mopcon 2019 32\"\n        src=\"/static/d8dbdefa26fda50e7ca4649104b1a560/8a6f4/mopcon-2019-32.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d8dbdefa26fda50e7ca4649104b1a560/51f8b/mopcon-2019-32.jpg 180w,\n/static/d8dbdefa26fda50e7ca4649104b1a560/5aea8/mopcon-2019-32.jpg 360w,\n/static/d8dbdefa26fda50e7ca4649104b1a560/8a6f4/mopcon-2019-32.jpg 720w,\n/static/d8dbdefa26fda50e7ca4649104b1a560/72109/mopcon-2019-32.jpg 1080w,\n/static/d8dbdefa26fda50e7ca4649104b1a560/92a9d/mopcon-2019-32.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>大大們都好強啊！右一 Ofa 是今年 MOPCON 的總召</p>\n<hr>\n<h3>閃電秀</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mopcon 2019 33\"\n        title=\"mopcon 2019 33\"\n        src=\"/static/1d2a070a2e4a1ed21687d4635d